# 3.1.1.research.external.q3.env-var-subscriptions

## question

which env var should apiKeyHelper set for subscription tokens?

## options

- `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` (standard api key)
- `ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN` (bearer token)
- `CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN` (subscription-specific)
- other?

## why it matters

determines which env var auth-pool must set for token injection.

## research approach

check claude cli source, test with different env vars, verify precedence.

## .status

awaited
